{"tid":640252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有個app可以rate返啲客就好","createTime":"2018-04-24T07:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T17:19:43.000Z","uid":120620,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b9badd8170f8efa6763419e1f0016b2cf96a2ef6","tid":640252,"uid":120620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:04:17.000Z","msg":"我係餐廳打份工<br />\n腦細就好鍾意搞啲優惠嘢<br />\n例如用邊個app book檯就有半價七折九折等<br />\n呢啲折通常會限左你食幾耐<br />\n有啲閪客遲到唔齊人又要遲走搞到成日返唔到檯<br />\n最sad既係你趕鳩佢佢又係個book檯app話鳩你<br />\n<br />\n如果有個app可以俾餐廳rate返個客<br />\n高rating有多啲優惠<br />\n少rating有少啲就好<br />\n咁就唔使個撚個當自己上帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b567895cb385fdb904b6f6d8943450fc6027e9","tid":640252,"uid":120620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:12:35.000Z","msg":"對住啲奉旨既閪客<br />\n真係好易燥<br />\n叫你走幾轉都冇所謂<br />\n一個問題問十鳩幾次都得<br />\n但係冇禮貌既就想大巴大巴車埋去"},{"pid":"d8dc9c565020c76c02b06e11df3fe1c09f8cab81","tid":640252,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"港豬閪係人都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52646cc40eae098b7120c4af039b710f8ac1159b","tid":640252,"uid":120620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8dc9c565020c76c02b06e11df3fe1c09f8cab81","tid":640252,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"港豬閪係人都知架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:17:23.000Z","msg":"所以有個互評既系統一定可以令啲貪小便宜既閪客自律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10160908f01023cda3236856efb3bbba14b78f8d","tid":640252,"uid":86283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"Black Mirror有一集係講差唔多既野"},{"pid":"020be155789bccb72105b9d9eef119bf31908fa6","tid":640252,"uid":120620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10160908f01023cda3236856ef